            <lg xml:id="TK431">
<l>cerukkuñ ciṉamuñ ciṟumaiyu millār</l>
<l> perukkam perumita nīrttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Truly great is the excellence of those (kings) who are free from pride, anger, and lust.</l>
            </lg>
